SUMMARY:Afternoon Salsa & Freestyle & More
DESCRIPTION:Salsa Valley Social. Daytime vibes. Legendary sound. No late night required. \nNot everyone wants to stay out till 2am or make the trip into the city just to feel the music. This Sunday afternoon is for those who still love to dance\, connect\, eat and enjoy great Latin and Freestyle music on their own time. \nJoin SVS at our new location: The Ellis in Newburgh\, NY. A beautifully renovated historic church turned stunning event space\, for an afternoon of Salsa\, Freestyle\, and more—set in a relaxed\, welcoming atmosphere where the focus is the music\, the people\, and the moment. \nSpinning the soundtrack are Norty Cotto\, former La Mega 97.9 on-air DJ and a true tastemaker of Latin\, Freestyle and Club dance floors\, alongside Zeno\, bringing his own unique flavor to the afternoon blending Salsa and Freestyle with his signature touch\, deep musical knowledge\, and seamless transitions that keep the dance floor alive. \nTogether\, expect class. \nEnjoy food from Beacon NY’s Smok’d.Kitchen and drinks on site because good music is always better with something great to sip and share. \nCome to dance\, sway to the rhythms\, or simply enjoy the vibe. Whether you’re meeting friends\, making new ones\, or just soaking it all in\, this is a grown\, feel-good Sunday experience. \nNo late night. No city stress. Just great music\, great people\, and a perfect Sunday afternoon.
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/afternoon-salsa-freestyle-more-2/
LOCATION:The Ellis\, 60 Dubois Street\, Newburgh\, NY\, United States
CATEGORIES:New York City
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/sunday-salsa-03-08-26.png
END:VEVENT
