SUMMARY:Salsa Sunday at La Chingona
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Salsa Sunday at La Chingona in Fort Worth and enjoy an afternoon of Latin dancing! The event will take place from 3 PM to 6 PM and feature salsa and bachata rhythms. Whether you’re a seasoned dancer or just starting out\, this event is perfect for anyone looking to have a great time. You don’t need to bring a partner to join the fun. Dance lessons begin at 3 PM. You will be among some of the most talented individuals in the dance community\, ensuring an amazing experience. This is a FREE EVENT\, giving you the chance to meet new people and enjoy yourself. See you there!\nFree parking at the Farrington Field parking lot (1.5 blocks south of La Chingona).
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/salsa-sunday-at-la-chingona/2026-03-08/
LOCATION:La Chingona\, 2800 Bledsoe St #100\, Fort Worth\, TX\, 76107\, United States
CATEGORIES:Dallas-Fort Worth
END:VEVENT
