SUMMARY:CLASSIC SALSA SUNDAY + INTERNATIONAL WOMENS DAY CELEBRATION
DESCRIPTION:Close your eyes and remember Sunday mornings at home. \n​You know the routine. \nYou didn’t wake up to an alarm. You woke up to the smell of Fabuloso and Café con Leche. \nYou heard the pots clanging in the kitchen before you even got out of bed. \nAnd above all\, you heard The Music. \n​It was Hector Lavoe telling a story. It was El Gran Combo making the walls vibrate. It was the soundtrack of our childhood. \n​That music didn’t just make us move; it made the house feel safe. It made the food taste better. It stayed in our blood. \n​This Sunday\, March 8th—on International Women’s Day—we bring that feeling back. \n​We are recreating the “Old School Sunday” for the women who raised us and the women who keep us going. No cleaning. No cooking. Just the joy. \n​THE VIBE: \n🎺 Live Music: Àmbito Latin Band playing the heavy hits that molded us. \n🎧 The DJ: DJ Pechocho spinning the vinyl classics that honor the real history of Salsa. \n🥘 The Kitchen: Open all day serving authentic homemade food (that tastes like Mami made it). \n​NO COVER CHARGE DETAILS:\n​Doors open at 3:00 PM.\n​Kitchen is firing all afternoon. \n​The vibe is 100% Clásica. \n​Bring the family. Bring la Doña. Let’s dance to the rhythm that raised us. \n​Date: Sunday\, March 8th\nLocation: 809 Lounge (3710 W Waters Ave\, Tampa) \n​#ClassicSalsaSunday #809Lounge #DiaDeLaMujer #HectorLavoe #SalsaVibes #TampaLatinos #MaloofEntertainment #OldSchoolSunday
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/classic-salsa-sunday-international-womens-day-celebration/
LOCATION:809 Lounge TAMPA\, 3710 W Waters Ave\, Tampa\, FL\, United States
CATEGORIES:Tampa
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/637822721_1240399101561179_1202296666738048126_n.jpg
END:VEVENT
